rows.label: bf08320100_0010
rows.name: It's too early to drop dead.

rows.label: bf08320100_0020
rows.name: We made it this far. I don't plan on giving up.

rows.label: bf08320100_0022
rows.name: Sorry man. If Judicium hadn't have gone down...

rows.label: bf08320100_0024
rows.name: ...we might have got you some better treatment.

rows.label: bf08320100_0026
rows.name: It's fine.

rows.label: bf08320100_0028
rows.name: When human cells are woven into the body of a Blade...

rows.label: bf08320100_0030
rows.name: ...they awaken strange abilities.

rows.label: bf08320100_0032
rows.name: That's good enough for me.

rows.label: bf08320100_0034
rows.name: This'll do fine.

rows.label: bf08320100_0036
rows.name: Even though she'd hate you for it... Right?

rows.label: bf08320100_0038
rows.name: I know Laura wouldn't have wanted this.

rows.label: bf08320100_0040
rows.name: Even so, I've got to keep my promise.

rows.label: bf08320100_0042
rows.name: All right. Then, I'll do the same.

rows.label: bf08320100_0044
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08320100_0046
rows.name:
Hey, Shin.
You better not get sentimental.

rows.label: bf08320100_0050
rows.name:
I found the ruins of
Iira down in Mors...

rows.label: bf08320100_0060
rows.name: Oh?

rows.label: bf08320100_0070
rows.name:
There were half-rotted Blades there.
Couldn't grow into Divine Beasts.

rows.label: bf08320100_0080
rows.name: They must've lived on for a while down there.

rows.label: bf08320100_0090
rows.name: A man once said, 'Live together with the humans.'

rows.label: bf08320100_0100
rows.name: Really, we were just living for the humans.

rows.label: bf08320100_0110
rows.name: Such is the truth, ordained for us by God.

rows.label: bf08320100_0120
rows.name: And that's the result.
